{
  "texts": [
    "This setup allows us to evaluate nuclei detection independently, disregarding the classification aspect.",
    "Weight balancing in the loss function is not applicable in this configuration due to the presence of only one class.",
    "In the second configuration, we grouped certain classes together.",
    "Specifically, we combined the classes Mitotic figure, Myoepithelium, Neutrophil, Normal epithelium, and Eosinophil into a single class labeled \"Other nuclei.\"",
    "Similarly, the classes Apoptotic body and Unlabeled were grouped under the class \"Ambiguous.\""
  ]
}